      • getNamespaces

        public final Map<String,String> getNamespaces()
                                       throws IllegalStateException
        Description copied from interface: Session
        Returns the modifiable namespace map of this Session. The map is backed by the default mappings of Data#getNamespaceMap(). New mappings are stored in the Session map and may override the default mappings. Removal of mappings is performed on the Session map, and may reactivate the default mapping as a consequence.
